benchmarks/**
# top-level CLAUDE.md only
!benchmarks/CLAUDE.md
# descend into each benchmark folder
!benchmarks/*/
# only README.md, VERSION.txt, and Phase 1 deferral markers in each benchmark
!benchmarks/*/README.md
!benchmarks/*/VERSION.txt
!benchmarks/*/DELETE.md
# phase grouping docs
!benchmarks/by-phase/
!benchmarks/by-phase/**/
!benchmarks/by-phase/**/README.md
